## Limitations

This report is based on a limited number of sources and may not capture the full spectrum of research on organic farming. The findings are primarily drawn from articles that focus on the negative aspects of organic agriculture, which may introduce bias. Additionally, the rapidly evolving nature of agricultural research means that newer studies could provide different insights not covered in this report.

